      "id": "PopularPost345565",
      "post_content": "The effect and a 3/3 body can be game-winning in the right situation, especially for only 4 mana. Bestow just makes it silly. Multiples bestowed upon one creature make it absolutely ridiculous, especially with an [Ethereal Armor](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ethereal Armor) or [Sphere of Safety](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sphere of Safety).  \n\"I attack with my [Hopeful Eidolon](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hopeful Eidolon), for 11 lifelinked damage. I also tap 2 of your blockers.\"  \n\"Ok, I'll take it. My turn, I attack with all these soldier tokens...\"  \n\"You gotta pay 4 mana for each of those, [Sphere of Safety](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sphere of Safety).\"  \n\"...\"",
      "posted_by": "SirLibraryEater",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost345565\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">The effect and a 3/3 body can be game-winning in the right situation, especially for only 4 mana. Bestow just makes it silly. Multiples bestowed upon one creature make it absolutely ridiculous, especially with an <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Ethereal Armor\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ethereal Armor\">Ethereal Armor</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Sphere of Safety\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sphere of Safety\">Sphere of Safety</a>.<br/>\"I attack with my <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Hopeful Eidolon\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hopeful Eidolon\">Hopeful Eidolon</a>, for 11 lifelinked damage. I also tap 2 of your blockers.\"<br/>\"Ok, I'll take it. My turn, I attack with all these soldier tokens...\"<br/>\"You gotta pay 4 mana for each of those, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Sphere of Safety\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sphere of Safety\">Sphere of Safety</a>.\"<br/>\"...\"</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '345565'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy91365\">SirLibraryEater</span>\r\n                                (10/11/2013 8:22:23 AM)\r\